{"tid":1420872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國新辦下午就香港問題舉行吹風會","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:15:36.000Z","uid":254880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1c92294abf8fe35716db18a035e401b940625d","tid":1420872,"uid":254880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】反對修訂《逃犯條例》的示威衝突持續不斷，昨日更升級至全港大罷工及不合作運動行動。國務院新聞辦公室今日下午2時30分舉行吹風會，由港澳辦新聞發言人楊光及徐露穎，講述對香港當前局勢的看法。<br />\n<br />\n國新辦昨日發通知，指今日就香港問題舉行媒體吹風會，邀請香港媒體採訪，但以場地限制為由，以聯合採訪形式進行，將以抽簽安排部分媒體採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔知今日會吹咩風</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d815d6eb80cb3647946a7bcaffed0de82c1f2664","tid":1420872,"uid":264455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:08:38.000Z","msg":"提防分化撚，勇武唔撚割，和理非都唔撚割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420725\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420725</a>"},{"pid":"7fb314ad0b953254c21ad51b238fcec2fc4e2de7","tid":1420872,"uid":157071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"有無直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dacff97489f381a9539c07a1a0e516407d07a16","tid":1420872,"uid":211941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"人肉錄音機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}